team-profile-large_header-1_content-right\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><p>Gulfraz Ahmed is a Senior Associate Licensed Conveyancer and Team Leader in our Landlord Financing &amp; Conveyancing team. Since joining us in 2013, he has built over a decade of experience advising on a broad range of property transactions.</p><p>‍</p><p>Gulfraz oversees a high-volume caseload focused on buy to let conveyancing. The team acts for both individuals and property companies on purchases, sales, and refinancing matters. Clients value their responsive approach, solution-focused mindset and clear, practical advice.</p><p>‍</p><p>Every transaction, whether involving a single property or a large portfolio, is managed with precision and a strong commitment to detail under Gulfraz’s leadership.</p><p>‍</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></header><section class=\"section_expertise-video w-condition-invisible\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"wrapper_wide-screen is-light\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"expertise-video_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid expertise-video_content\"><div class=\"expertise-video_content-left\"><h2 class=\"w-dyn-bind-empty\"></h2><p class=\"w-dyn-bind-empty\"></p></div><div class=\"expertise-video_content-right\"><div class=\"expertise-image_wrapper\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/plugins/Basic/assets/placeholder.60f9b1840c.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" class=\"image w-dyn-bind-empty\"></div><a href=\"/gulfraz-ahmed#\" class=\"expertise-video_lightbox w-inline-block w-dyn-bind-empty w-lightbox\"><img src=\"gulfraz-ahmed.html\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" class=\"expertise-video_lightbox-image w-dyn-bind-empty\"><div class=\"lightbox-play-icon\"><div class=\"icon-embed-large w-embed\"><svg width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M5.33301 32C5.33301 17.2724